### Phase 3: Raw Responses to Parquet

Convert `raw-responses.jsonl` ‚Üí `raw-responses.parquet` for efficient querying:

```sql
COPY (
  SELECT 
    metadata.queryType,
    metadata.timestamp,
    metadata.owner,
    metadata.repo,
    response
  FROM read_json_auto('raw-responses.jsonl', format='newline_delimited')
